org.firebirdsql.jdbc.parser

Interface JaybirdSqlListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    JaybirdSqlBaseListener

    public interface JaybirdSqlListener
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by JaybirdSqlParser.
